name: Steering Wheel Latex
des: The MOMO MOD. 30 racing steering wheel is ideal for Sedan and GT car drivers looking for maximum control. The anatomic design features black anodized spokes and thumb rests to better fit a driver’s grip preference. The MOD. 30's flat bottom design makes entering and exiting a vehicles cockpit easier while increasing leg clearance especially for when quicker steering is required instead of full rotation of the wheel.
